---
title: Creamy Red Lentil, Pumpkin & Coconut Soup with Baby Broccoli, Yoghurt & Garlic Tortilla Chips
description: We’re eating the rainbow tonight, well, the first half of it at least! Simmer red lentils in a creamy soup with hints of coconut and our mild North Indian spice blend. Add orange roasted kumara plus baby broccoli, for that vibrant pop of green. Remember to soak it up with garlic tortilla chips.
